---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Quality & Regulatory Compliance Hub | Egypt Alumin" 
  description="Exacting B2B quality standards. ISO 9001:2015 certified, REACH registered, and CBAM-ready. Review our chemical testing procedures, optical spectrometry, and SGS verification."
  lang="en"
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/en/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">Quality & Compliance</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="product-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-hero-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Zero-Defect B2B Standards</span>
          <h1 style="font-size: 3.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;">Quality & Regulatory Compliance Hub</h1>
          <p class="product-hero-lead" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">
            Delivering absolute chemical consistency, strict dimensional tolerances, and verified ecological footprints 
            for European automotive foundries, extruders, and rolling mills.
          </p>
          <div class="product-hero-badges" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 1.8rem;">
            <span>ISO 9001:2015 Certified</span>
            <span>REACH Registered</span>
            <span>CBAM Compliant</span>
            <span>EN 10204 3.1 Certified</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       PILLARS OF TRUST
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0 3rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; max-width:700px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;">
        <h2>The Core Pillars of Our Quality Regime</h2>
        <p>We combine advanced laboratory testing, external certification audits, and modern tracking software to guarantee that every single shipment conforms precisely to European standards.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div class="app-item" style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🔬</div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Chemical Traceability</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft);">
            Every melt undergoes Optical Emission Spectrometry (OES). We stamp heat numbers directly onto individual 20kg and 25kg ingots, establishing unbroken traceability back to raw feedstock.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="app-item" style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🛡️</div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Regulatory Readiness</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft);">
            Fully REACH registered for the European Union. Standardized, quarterly audited carbon disclosures conform to the final EU-CBAM reporting requirements for Scope 1 & 2 emissions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="app-item" style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🚢</div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">SGS Independent Audits</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft);">
            To offer absolute peace of mind, we welcome third-party inspections (SGS, Bureau Veritas, TÜV) at the loading port of Alexandria to verify bundle count, dimensions, and chemical analysis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       TESTING PROCEDURES
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--silver-soft); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center;">
        <div class="product-image" style="box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);">
          <div class="product-img-container-inner" style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
            <img src="/images/hero/1.4-aluminium-quality-control-laboratory-testing.webp" alt="Aluminium Quality Testing" class="product-img-modern" style="width:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Zero Defect Execution</span>
          <h2>Rigorous Laboratory & Structural Testing</h2>
          <p>
            At our 50,000 m² state-of-the-art facility, we perform standard and custom testing regimes to fulfill
            automotive Tier-1 PPAP specifications:
          </p>
          <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin: 1.5rem 0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem;">
            <li style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; font-size:0.95rem;">
              <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:bold;">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Optical Emission Spectrometry (OES):</strong> Full 21-element breakdown checked multiple times per heat cycle to verify strict impurity limits (e.g., Fe ≤ 0.15% on premium grades).
              </div>
            </li>
            <li style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; font-size:0.95rem;">
              <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:bold;">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Hydrogen Gas Testing:</strong> In-line rotary degassers lower dissolved hydrogen content to ≤ 0.12 ml / 100g Al, measured via dynamic vacuum solidifying tests.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; font-size:0.95rem;">
              <span style="color:var(--teal); font-weight:bold;">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Microstructure Modification:</strong> Precise additions of Strontium (Sr) or Sodium (Na) to modify silicon grain structure, enhancing alloy ductility and elongation.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       STANDARDS COMPLIANCE TABLE
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; max-width:700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;">
        <h2>Global Standards Concordance</h2>
        <p>Our aluminium ingots are certifiably aligned with all primary European, American, and Asian specifications, simplifying compliance for global B2B procurement offices.</p>
      </div>

      <table class="spec-table" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Product Category</th>
            <th>European (EN)</th>
            <th>US Equivalent (AA)</th>
            <th>Japanese (JIS)</th>
            <th>Chinese (GB/T)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Primary Ingot</strong></td>
            <td>EN 576 (Al99.7)</td>
            <td>P1020A</td>
            <td>JIS H 2102</td>
            <td>GB/T 1196 (Al99.70)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Die-Casting Alloy</strong></td>
            <td>EN AC-46000</td>
            <td>A383 / 380</td>
            <td>JIS H 5302 (ADC12)</td>
            <td>GB/T 15115 (YL113)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Silicon Premium</strong></td>
            <td>EN AC-42000 / 43500</td>
            <td>A356 / A360</td>
            <td>JIS H 5202 (AC4C)</td>
            <td>GB/T 1173 (ZL101)</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       COMPLIANCE & CBAM DOWNLOADS
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="cbam" aria-labelledby="downloads-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center; gap: 4rem;">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Verified B2B Documentation</span>
          <h2 id="downloads-heading">Download Quality Certificates & Sample MTCs</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Gain instant access to our accredited ISO documentation, REACH statement files, 
            and a sample EN 10204 3.1 Material Test Certificate (MTC) showing element-by-element spectral analysis.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem;">
            <a href="/assets/sample-mtc-en-10204.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:fit-content;">
              Download Sample MTC (PDF)
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M19 12l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/assets/iso-9001-certificate.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width:fit-content; border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); color:white;">
              Download ISO 9001:2015 Cert
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
          <h4 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; color:var(--amber); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size:1.1rem;">European Import Compliance Checklist:</h4>
          <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.9rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
            <li>✓ REACH Registration Number</li>
            <li>✓ EU customs EORI validation framework</li>
            <li>✓ Scope 1 & 2 CO₂ Embedded Emissions report</li>
            <li>✓ SGS Alexandria Loading Port Certificate</li>
            <li>✓ EN 10204 Type 3.1 Inspection Certificate</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FINAL CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Direct Sales Technical Desk</span>
      <h2>Have customized technical requirements?</h2>
      <p>Whether you require narrowed composition windows, custom heat bundle counts, or modified grain refiner quantities, speak directly with Noel Murphy.</p>
      <div class="final-cta-actions">
        <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Request Custom Sample</a>
        <a href="tel:+353871187806" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Noel: +353 87 118 7806</a>
      </div>
      <p class="final-cta-direct">
        Direct Email: <a href="mailto:noel@egyptalumin.com">noel@egyptalumin.com</a> · WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806">Direct Chat</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .product-img-container-inner {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .product-img-modern {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .product-img-container-inner:hover .product-img-modern {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
</style>
